## Media assets captured

### Hero flow documentation
Successfully recorded and screenshotted the complete factoring lifecycle:

**Scene 1: Carrier Invoice Submission**
- 01-01_carrier_dashboard.png — role context (Sam Trucking LLC, Carrier role)
- 02-02_invoice_list.png — 5 seed invoices in various states (PENDING, APPROVED, DISBURSED, REJECTED, COLLECTED); all amounts shown in proper currency (integer cents); "Submit Invoice" button visible
- 03-03_invoice_form.png — carrier-facing invoice submission form with 8 input fields

**Scene 2: Underwriter Approval & Disbursal**
- 04-06_underwriter_dashboard.png — role context (Jordan Lee, Underwriter role)
- 05-07_approval_queue.png — Approval Queue showing pending and approved invoices; INV-001 (Swift Logistics, $12,500.00 face value) pending review; INV-002 (Northern Freight Co., $8,750.00 face value) approved with Advance ($7,437.50) and Fee ($262.50) calculated and displayed in integer cents; colored action buttons (Approve/Reject for pending, Disburse for approved)
- 06-08_invoice_approved.png — invoice status transitioned to APPROVED after underwriter approval
- 07-09_invoice_disbursed.png — invoice status transitioned to DISBURSED after disbursal (shows Collect button now visible)

**Scene 3: Admin Ledger & Accounting**
- 08-10_admin_dashboard.png — role context (Admin role)
- 09-11_chart_of_accounts.png — Chart of Accounts showing seed balances across CASH_BANK ($49.98M), FACTORING_RECEIVABLE, FEE_REVENUE, CARRIER_RESERVE_HOLDBACK accounts
- 10-12_ledger_entries.png — Double-Entry Ledger showing 7 recent entries for INV-003 (Prime Haul Partners) and INV-005 (Eagle Transport); each entry shows DATE, DESCRIPTION (e.g., "Advance disbursed - INV-003 Prime Haul Partners"), TYPE (DEBIT in green, CREDIT in blue), AMOUNT (all in proper currency format), and INVOICE reference; summary shows Total Debits ($56,785.00) and Total Credits ($55,285.00) for this view; footer describes FIDC Double-Entry Model including debit/credit logic and notation that "all amounts stored as integer minor units — no floating-point on money paths"
- 11-13_ledger_detail.png — scrolled ledger view showing additional entries and full accounting trail

