## Design & content captured

All media reflects the bespoke Brazilian fintech design direction:
- Dark theme (navy/ink base, fintech-grade contrast)
- Clean data tables with role-aware context (user avatar + role shown in footer)
- Color-coded status badges (PENDING in orange, APPROVED in green, DISBURSED in purple, REJECTED in red, COLLECTED in cyan)
- Integer-cents money format throughout (no floats)
- Monospaced numerals and proper currency formatting
- Fintech-appropriate typography and spacing
- Zero em/en dashes in any visible text

Screenshots show:
- Full financial workflow: invoice intake → underwriter approval + disbursal → ledger recording
- Money correctness: advance ($7,437.50), fee ($262.50), face value ($8,750.00) all calculated and displayed in proper minor units
- RBAC in action: different screens and controls for carrier, underwriter, and admin roles
- Real auth: each screenshot includes role context (user name + role badge)
- Production-quality polish: no console errors, responsive layout, professional UX

