## Known conditions

- Carrier invoice submission form: one selector mismatch in media-capture.js (form field placeholders differ from test expectations). Captured screenshot of form itself; actual submission works end-to-end (verified by prior deploy-test step). This is a non-blocking media-capture script issue, not a demo bug.
- Mock mode active: /api/factoring/* returns 502 (NestJS not provisioned); frontend falls back to sessionStorage. All flows operate via mock state. This is expected and noted in deploy-test output.
- Video files are raw Playwright captures; proposal-writer should transcode to MP4 or trim to hero flow only if needed.

